Description:
The largest two bedroom retreat in the coveted Conder
The largest two bedroom apartment in the exclusive Conder building which also comes with two bathrooms and two secure car spaces, this exclusive NewQuay precinct opportunity is one not to be missed.
An enormous 113 sqm (approx.) of space makes this a truly rare offering
Uninterrupted views of Victoria Harbour from balcony, living, and bedrooms
Immense central lounge and dining with superb light and timber floors
Generous master bedroom with ample BIRs, ensuite, and balcony access
Stone and timber kitchen with s/steel appliances overlooks the vast central zone
Immaculate bathrooms
Separate laundry room
Ducted heating and cooling, intercom entry
Storage cage
AMENITIES
The Conder complex offers residents access to an onsite building manager, pool, gym and outdoor recreation area.
LOCATION
Youre a short walk to The District Docklands which offers Hoyts Cinemas, amazing Eight Street hawker food outlets, and a new fresh food precinct opening soon called The Market which will deliver an array of butchers, delis, bakeries, coffee roasters, Woolworths supermarket, and Dan Murphys. Youre also near Marvel Stadium perfect for footy fans, Capital City Trail, leading universities, nearby trams including the free City Circle line, Southern Cross Station, and the Skybus to Melbourne Airport.

Description:
An Elegant Entry Level Pad in the Coveted Quays
An appealing option for city professionals and eager investors thanks to smart modern style and a spot in the exclusive Quays complex, this one bedroom + study apartment is an affordable piece of the vibrant Docklands life.
The Quays complex offers memorable facilities from a Health Club featuring a swimming pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium and a yoga studio, to the Residents Club on Level One with a library, reading room, business centre, boardroom, private dining room & cinema lounge. There is also a rooftop garden with BBQ and dining facilities.
The complex is also located in the excellent NewQuay precinct which is renowned for its close proximity to attractions that include the District Docklands Shopping Centre, Waterfront City with Costco and Melbourne Star Observation Wheel, Medibank Icehouse, and the 70 tram which takes you to the city, MCG, Richmond, Hawthorn, and Box Hill. You can also walk to Woolshed pub, Cargo and Sir Basil.
The residence itself is low-maintenance, offers a clever open floorplan, and oozes contemporary style. A relaxed living/meals zone opens to the quiet balcony with a north-westerly aspect, with this balcony also accessed via the comfortable bedroom boasting a mirrored built-in robe. An open study just off the entry is a versatile space, meanwhile the well-appointed kitchen enjoys a glass splashback, stone benchtop, and stainless steel appliances.
Other extras include a stylish bathroom, European laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, and secure intercom entry. Dont miss out on this wonderful Quays opportunity!
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0437 092 078 to arrange an exclusive inspection

Description:
Enviable Style and Inspired City Views
This impressive tower apartment has the best floor plan in the building and is situated on level 17 of the popular Nolan complex. Representing the ultimate in modern high-rise living, it is complemented by resort type amenities including heated pool, fully equipped gym & common room, this apartment offers a rare opportunity to move in and enjoy premium level living in New Quay, Docklands, with the CBD, public transport, shopping, cafes and bars at your door step.
The apartment features two spacious bedrooms: the master with WIR, en-suite and private balcony. The second with large BIRs and access to the main wraparound balcony with unrestricted views over New Quay Marina and the City.
There is a central second bathroom with shower, spacious open plan living/dining area adjoining the gourmet kitchen with prestige black stone bench tops, quality Smeg s/steel appliances and ample storage. Other fantastic features include ducted heating & cooling, 2 secure side by side car spaces, laundry room, storage cage, security intercom, wired internet and cable TV connections.

Description:
Breathtaking sub penthouse living with spectacular views
One of Yarras Points shining jewels sitting high on the 30th floor and offering exceptional views of the CBD, picturesque marina, and northern ranges, this outstanding 3 bedroom + study, 2 bathroom, 2 car space sub penthouse apartment is the epitome of stylish, elegant, and spacious Docklands living.
An expansive central lounge and dining zone is open and free-flowing, and has access out to the generous north-east facing balcony where the unforgettable views can be seen day and night. The immaculate kitchen is heaven for home cooks and is fitted with premium stone along with the finest of Miele appliances including a steam oven plus an integrated fridge and freezer.
All three bedrooms have the north-east orientation and take in the excellent views including the master bedroom which also boasts a walk-in robe and sublime dual vanity ensuite. One of the other bedrooms has entry out to the balcony and is steps to the study area with built-in desk. Further enjoy a deluxe central bathroom, laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, storage cage, and access to RekDek with gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
The Yarras Point building sits in a peaceful yet convenient part of the Yarras Edge precinct, which is close to South Wharf Promenade delivering excellent restaurants and bars incluidng The General Assembly, Charlie Lovett, Munich Brauhaus and The Boatbuilders Yard. Youre also a short walk to the DFO shopping, CBD and Southbank attractions, Crown Casino, trams, and Southern Cross Station.

Description:
Simply stunning apartment living.
Perfectly placed on a podium level in amongst a boutique 4-floor section, this stunning high-end apartment is positioned for a convenient and contemporary lifestyle.
On the doorstep to the abundance of shopping, entertainment and transport options associated with the incredible Docklands quarter, this spectacular abode is located between the north and south towers, taking in amazing west-facing views to the surrounding tree-lined streets.
An intricate layout includes towering high ceilings, wooden floorboards and a sparkling open plan living, dining and kitchen precinct flooded with natural light.
Impressive from start to finish, the kitchen incorporates stone benchtops and splash back, built-in stainless steel appliances including dishwasher, plenty of storage and a feature Island bench and breakfast bar.
Complimenting the modern tones enjoyed throughout the home, the sleek bathroom has a separate shower and brilliant inset bath while a European laundry is easily accessible from 2 bedrooms with robes, the master also including its own matching en-suite.
A private outdoor area is a place to sit, relax and entertain while ducted heating and cooling, double glazed windows and a same level carpark with storage box are valued additions to a simply unrivalled offering.
Positioned in a superior complex with its own swimming pool, gymnasium, spa, sauna and function room, apartment living does not come any better.

Sophisticated, stylish and delightfully driven by high-end quality, this striking 2 bedroom apartment seamlessly connects an ultra-modern interior with an oversized exterior. This one will not last long!

Description:
Stunning harbour views and spacious light-filled living
If you value light-filled living space, stunning westerly views including Victoria Harbour, and a practical layout that allows for relaxed days and nights, then this wonderful 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment in the exclusive Victoria Tower is yours to embrace.
Sun fills the generous central living and dining zone which has full height windows allowing for the brilliant views which also includes the tranquil Docklands Park. The kitchen is splashed with beautiful stone and comes with an island bench and full stainless steel appliances perfect for eager home cooks.
Both bedrooms enjoy built-in robes including the master bedroom which promises a sleek dual vanity ensuite. This special master bedroom also has access to the large undercover balcony which is the perfect outdoor retreat also with amazing views. Further enjoy a stylish bathroom, European laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom entry, and secure car space. The property also enjoys 96 sqm (approx.) internal space!
Residents are lucky enough to have access to a gymnasium and a building manager. Youre also close to Marvel Stadium, Bourke Street restaurants and cafes, The Hub @ Docklands, Docklands Park, Harbour Esplanade trams, and Southern Cross Station.
Please contact Serena Su on 0499 083 362 to arrange an exclusive inspection

Description:
"Magnificent 270 degree water-views!"
This fantastic 16th floor 3 bedroom apartment is located in the prestigious "Dock 5" residential complex and has the most amazing views of Docklands' marinas, the bay, Bolte bridge and further on to Melbourne's northern and western suburbs. "Beautiful by day, fairy land by night !" The finishes and fixtures of this superior apartment are of the highest quality - the hallmark of Dock 5 and the views are breathtaking. On offer are 3 spacious bedrooms each with built in robes and the main having a stylish ensuite including deep soaking tub whilst the other two share the contemporary bathroom. The gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances, stone benchtops, breakfast bar and butler's pantry adjoins the open plan living area opening onto the wide wrap-around balcony perfect for entertaining or just relaxing. Other features include study nook, 2 secure undercover car spaces, european style laundry, ducted a/c-heating, heated pool and gymnasium as well as internal gardens and your own personal refrigerated wine cellar completes this package of what dreams are made of !!!
For an inspection of this truly elite property that is approx. 186 sqm call Glenn Donnelly on 0419 998 235

Description:
Waterfront Living!
Apartment is featured with stone kitchen which is completed with sleek black tapware and stainless steel appliances. Built in wardrobes can be found in the bedroom and bathroom fitted with rain shower and laundry.
In a city famous for its great food and thriving café culture, residents will be spoilt for choice with a wide selection of places to eat, drink & entertain at your doorstep.
Sitting right in the heart of Docklands on the fringe of Melbourne's CBD, this location enjoys access to a variety of public amenities; in particular, Harbour Town Shopping District, Harbour Ferry, Melbourne Star Observation Wheel, Direct Factory Outlet, City Circle Tram, Capital City Bicycle Trail, a short stroll to Southern Cross Station and only a short tram ride to RMIT University, the University of Melbourne, the State Library and Bourke Street Mall, as well as a myriad of bars, restaurants and cafes.
Positioned on Victoria Harbour, overlooking Melbourne's skyline and the ever-changing marina. This complex offers a tranquil escape from the nearby bustling city.
Residents will enjoy a thoughtful array of tailored facilities meeting requirements of business and pleasure with access to the stunning 25-meter indoor Swimming Pool, Spa, Sauna, lounge, Library, fully equipped gymnasium, as well as the resident's rooftop garden located on level 5 that features beautiful BBQ & Picnic areas perfect for all year round entertaining!
The apartment also boasts some of the most indulgent views and bespoke interior design that is sure to take your breath away.
Please contact Mo Mellak on 0405 083 188 to find out more and to arrange a viewing.

Description:
Sleek 23rd floor living in the coveted Quays building
Looking for a spot in the brilliant Quays complex which offers memorable recreational facilities and impressive modern flair? Look no further than this 1 bedroom apartment located on the 23rd floor!
A low-maintenance property that will suit both keen investors, CBD professionals, and 1st home purchasers
Enjoys a westerly orientation and open living and dining zone
Tiled kitchen area with stone benchtops and s/steel appliances
Relaxed bedroom with BIR and access out to the covered balcony
Immaculate bathroom with designer mosaic tiling and laundry
Reverse cycle heating and cooling
Secure intercom entry
Secure car space
AMENITIES
The Quays features a Health Club with a pool, spa, sauna, gym and yoga studio, Residents Club on Level One with a library, reading room, business centre, boardroom, private dining room & cinema lounge, and a rooftop garden with BBQ and dining facilities.
LOCATION
This part of the NewQuay precinct gives you convenient access to Digital Harbour, Stadium precinct, and Victoria Harbour precinct. Youre close to The District Docklands with Hoyts Cinemas, 8 Street hawker food outlets, and a new fresh food precinct opening soon called The Market which will offer an array of butchers, delis, bakeries, coffee roasters, Woolworths supermarket, and Dan Murphys. Youre also near restaurants including Woolshed and Mama Rumaan, Marvel Stadium, Capital City Trail, nearby trams including the free City Circle line, Southern Cross Station, and Skybus.

Encompassing a huge master bedroom with walk in robes and ensuite with his and her basins, second bedroom with mirrored built in robes, central bathroom with full sized bath and separate shower, massive kitchen with walk in pantry and a massive open plan living/dining area perfect for entertainers make this home one not to be looked over.
